text: Haarlemmerliede en Spaarnwoude is a former municipality in the Dutch province of North Holland. Since 2019, it has been part of the municipality of Haarlemmermeer. The former municipality had a population of 5,760 in August 2017. Category:21st-century disestablishments in the Netherlands Category:Former municipalities of North Holland Category:Haarlemmermeer
title: Haarlemmerliede en Spaarnwoude
